reviewText: This has changed my life. Not only has lengthened my core by six inches, the pelvis tilt has made my squatty potty no longer necessary. I am now the best dressed at the gum as I have received many fashion tips from watching the film. (E.g. fishnets and false eye lashes.) If you want to become a well-rounded woman or receive an excellent white elephant gift, this is the artistic production for you. Thank you to my grandma Betty for this exercise motivator.
